text.section:
On written request of an exclusive representative, for each employee in the bargaining unit represented by the exclusive representative, the University System of Maryland system institutions, Morgan State University, St. Mary's College of Maryland, and Baltimore City Community College shall provide the exclusive representative with the employee's:
name;
position classification;
unit;
home and work site addresses where the employee receives interoffice or United States mail; and
home and work site telephone numbers.
